Phase 4 -  Testing and Validation
---------------------------------

Security Activities
• Dynamic security testing
• Penetration testing (could opt in for continuous testing with Third party)
• Security acceptance testing
• Vulnerability assessment
• API security testing

Tools & Technologies
• DAST: Burp Suite, OWASP ZAP, Acunetix
• Penetration testing: Metasploit, Kali Linux tools
• API testing: Postman, SoapUI with security tests
• Fuzz testing: AFL, Peach Fuzzer
• Container scanning: Trivy, Clair, Anchore

Methodologies & Standards
• OWASP Testing Guide
• PTES (Penetration Testing Execution Standard)
• OWASP Top 10 validation
• API security testing (OWASP API Top 10)
• Red team exercises

Key Deliverables
• Penetration test report
• Vulnerability assessment results
• Remediation plan
• Security test cases passed
• Risk acceptance documentation
